OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FThe
OL,6,Fweather should remain fine on Friday
OL,7,Fand much of Saturday with further very
OL,8,Fwarm sunshine. Potentially turning
OL,9,Fcooler and breezier on Sunday with
OL,10,Frain possible.
